# SIXMEN — Architecture Envelope

> `docs/erp/core/04_Architecture.md` §3.1, §3.12–§3.13 · `docs/erp/phases/GD0_Nen_tang/07_Sequence_Diagram.md` §0.1 · `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/07_Sequence_Diagram.md` §0.1 · `sixmen-laravel-backend.mdc`

## Memory Scope

This rule must keep active:

- **Scope governed:** mutation envelope, critical domain guards (single-entry), reporting boundary.
- **Canonical context:** `docs/erp/core/04_Architecture.md` · `docs/erp/phases/GD0_Nen_tang/07_Sequence_Diagram.md` §0.1 · `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/07_Sequence_Diagram.md` §0.1 · `sixmen-laravel-backend.mdc`.
- **Required project memory:** `InventoryService` · `MaterialInventoryService` · `DocumentNumberService` · `CogsService` · FormRequest/Policy · append-only movement · `pgsql_reporting` read-only for mutation.
- **Deprecated / rejected:** direct balance update · manual doc codes · business logic in Controller/Filament/Livewire/Blade · mutation on reporting connection · liệt kê mọi CRUD service như critical guard.
- **Applies to:** mọi business mutation backend/frontend gọi service.
- **Does not apply to:** read-only `*ReportService` / dashboard query (vẫn không mutate trên `pgsql_reporting`).
- **Conflict handling:** defer `sixmen-data-safety` cho audit/append-only; defer `sixmen-governance` cho schema/service mới vào critical guards (cần ADR).
- **Stop condition:** bypass critical service · mutation thiếu Policy/transaction · schema change không có migration-note.

## Envelope mọi mutation

```
User action (Filament / Livewire / API)
  → route/action
  → FormRequest / validation
  → EnsureBranchScope (+ legal_entity scope)
  → Policy::authorize
  → Domain Service
  → DB::transaction (if multi-table)
  → Activity Log (audit)
  → Event / notification (if cross-module)
  → Test (Pest: happy + 403)
```

- Business mutation → **Service** — không logic trong Controller / Filament Resource / Livewire / Blade.
- Do **not** import across module boundaries unless public Service/Event is defined.

## Critical domain guards

> Khóa **critical single-entry boundaries** — bypass có thể sai tồn, sai mã chứng từ, sai giá vốn, mất audit/truy vết.
> **Không thêm mọi service vào đây.** Service mới chỉ thêm khi ADR/Architecture Decision xác nhận critical single-entry.

- **Finished-goods inventory** — chỉ `InventoryService`; không update trực tiếp `inventory`; movement + balance cùng transaction; append-only.
- **Material/NPL inventory** — chỉ `MaterialInventoryService`; không update trực tiếp `material_inventory_balances`.
- **Document numbering** — chỉ `DocumentNumberService` (PO/GRN/ADJ/TRF/LSX/HDNT/BBGN); transaction + `FOR UPDATE`; override → permission + audit.
- **COGS / costing** — chỉ `CogsService` hoặc costing service đã duyệt ADR; không tính rải rác UI/controller/report.
- **Input validation** — mutation input qua `FormRequest` / validated DTO; không `$request->all()` ghi DB.
- **Policy / scope** — mọi mutation qua Policy; UI ẩn button **không** thay backend authorization.
- **Movement / audit append-only** — `inventory_movements`, `material_inventory_movements`, `activity_log`, audit logs; không UPDATE/DELETE để “sửa lỗi” → reversal/adjustment/cancel/exception (`sixmen-data-safety.mdc`).
- **Reporting connection** — mutation/transaction/`FOR UPDATE`/critical services → **primary only**; `pgsql_reporting` chỉ report/dashboard/export đã duyệt; fresh data → `force_primary`.
- **Request observability** — important mutations should carry `request_id` and request timing metadata where available: `duration_ms`, `db_query_count`, `db_time_ms`, `memory_peak_mb`. Request timing ≠ Activity Log — xem GĐ0 `07_Sequence_Diagram.md` §0.1.

### Thêm service mới vào block này khi

Kiểm soát tồn/movement · mã chứng từ/sequence/lock · tiền/COGS/thanh toán · audit/pháp lý/khớp hồ sơ · permission scope CTY-HKD/kho · ADR đánh dấu single-entry.

| Future *(chưa active guard)* | Khi nào thêm |
|------------------------------|--------------|
| `PaymentRequestService` | Payment request có duyệt/thanh toán thật |
| `DocumentMatchService` | Khớp hồ sơ / `pending_docs` là gate vận hành |
| `StockReservationService` | Giữ tồn / reserve đơn sàn |
| `ChannelSyncService` | Sync đơn/sản phẩm sàn TMĐT |
| `ReturnService` | Hoàn hàng ảnh hưởng tồn/tiền/chứng từ |
| `PricingService` | Giá bán/khuyến mãi rule tập trung |

### Không thêm vào critical guards

CRUD/helper thông thường — bypass không hỏng dữ liệu lõi: `BrandService`, `ColorService`, `SizeService`, `SupplierService`, `ProductService` CRUD cơ bản, `NotificationService`, `ExportExcelService`, `DashboardCardService`, `*ReportService` / `DashboardQueryService` *(read-only query — không mutation)*.

Vẫn tuân: business mutation qua Service; không logic trong Controller/Filament/Livewire/Blade.

## Trước / sau implement

**Trước:** `task-brief.md` · skill đúng vai trò · source of truth đúng phạm vi (ERD / workflow / AC) — **báo rõ file đã đọc**; không quét toàn repo. `architecture-impact.md` (if logic/DB/quyền) · `migration-note.md` (if schema).

**Sau:** Pest happy + **403** (+ 422 if API) · `architecture-compliance-checklist.md` · Human Owner gate if schema/rule/≥2 module/prod.

## Cấm tuyệt đối

- Bypass critical services: `InventoryService`, `MaterialInventoryService`, `DocumentNumberService`, `CogsService`
- Manual `DELETE`/`TRUNCATE`/`DROP` on production (`sixmen-data-safety.mdc`)
- Mutation on `pgsql_reporting`
- Migration without `migration-note.md` + approval
- React/Vue SPA `frontend/` for admin GĐ0–3
